OL,4,Coil rig blast 'woeful' sentence for
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FThe family of a South Tyneside man
OL,8,Fkilled while working on an oil rig in
OL,9,Fthe Persian gulf have branded the
OL,10,Fsentence handed to his killer "woeful".
OL,12,FRobbie Robson, who was 48, was beaten
OL,13,Fto death by his roommate Scott Forrest
OL,14,Fusing an iron weight aboard an oil rig
OL,15,Foff the coast of Qatar.
OL,17,FThe family of Mr Robson, who was from
OL,18,FCleadon, in Tyne and Wear, were
OL,19,Foriginally told that Forrest could
OL,20,Fface the death penalty if Qatari
OL,21,Fcourts found him guilty of murder.
