OL,3,CFamily of man bludgeoned to death on
OL,4,Coil rig blast 'woeful' sentence for
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FHowever, during legal proceedings in
OL,8,FDecember, he was convicted of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter and given a sentence of
OL,10,Ften years.
OL,12,FAn appeal against that sentence is
OL,13,Funderway with an outcome likely to be
OL,14,Fknown on Thursday 2 May.
OL,16,FThe family saw a previous appeal
OL,17,Frejected in January and have been told
OL,18,Fthat these proceedings will be the
OL,19,Flast in relation to the case.
