OL,3,CFamily of man bludgeoned to death on
OL,4,Coil rig blast 'woeful' sentence for
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"As a family we have had to read all
OL,8,Fthe detailed reports into what
OL,9,Fhappened that evening and it is
OL,10,Fsomething we would wish on no other
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,F"We place great faith that the Qatari
OL,14,Fjustice system will agree, following
OL,15,Fthis final appeal, that the woeful
OL,16,Fsentence imposed needs to be
OL,17,Freconsidered not only to get true
OL,18,Fjustice for Robbie, but to send a
OL,19,Fmessage to the world."
