OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FThe family is also making a civil
OL,8,Fclaim against Mr Robson's employer,
OL,9,Ffollowing new details which emerged
OL,10,Fduring the trial.
OL,12,FMs Graham, who has a two-year-old son
OL,13,Fwith Mr Robson, said: "Robbie was an
OL,14,Famazing, one-of-a-kind, beautiful
OL,15,Fsoul. He was a loving partner, dad,
OL,16,Fson, brother and uncle whose life was
OL,17,Ftaken too soon.
OL,19,F"Robbie was irreplaceable and he is
OL,20,Fsorely missed by everyone that knew
OL,21,Fhim.
OL,26,@uD@WOU
