OL,3,CFamily of man bludgeoned to death on
OL,4,Coil rig blast 'woeful' sentence for
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"The initial charge of murder should
OL,8,Fbe upheld, given the choice between
OL,9,Fonly ten years' imprisonment or a life
OL,10,Fsentence ` we'd, of course, fully
OL,11,Fendorse the latter.
OL,13,F"We were told to prepare for the death
OL,14,Fpenalty to be handed down, so to
OL,15,Freceive the news of a ten-year
OL,16,Fsentence was incomprehensible.
OL,18,F"A more severe punishment should be
OL,19,Fimposed to reflect the gravity of the
OL,20,Fcrime and the loss our family endures."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU|D@gO]
