OL,4,Coil rig blast 'woeful' sentence for
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FMr Robson had been working for
OL,8,FAberdeenshire-based underwater
OL,9,Finspection company Film-Ocean, on the
OL,10,FSeafox Burj gas rig when he was killed
OL,11,Fin December 2022.
OL,13,FForrest, who is 43 and from Maud,
OL,14,FAberdeenshire, hit him about 20 times
OL,15,Fwith the weight which was used in
OL,16,Fsubmarines, the victim's family said.
OL,18,FForrest, who also attacked a co-
OL,19,Fworker, was believed to be suffering
OL,20,Ffrom stress and anxiety at the time,
OL,21,Fcaused by living in cramped conditions.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
