OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FPatrick Maguire, partner at law firm
OL,8,FHCC which represents Ms Graham, said:
OL,9,F"The family has not only been through
OL,10,Fthe heartache of losing Robbie but
OL,11,Fhave had to endure the experience of
OL,12,Fseeing the perpetrator receive a
OL,13,Fsentence far less than they and others
OL,14,Fexpect in circumstances like this.
OL,16,F"We can confirm that we have been
OL,17,Finstructed by the family to begin the
OL,18,Fprocess of bringing a civil action
OL,19,Fagainst Robbie's employers which will
OL,20,Fbegin in the next few days."
